Per default the tooltip uses the xAxis label of a point which returns ```undefined``` when there&#39;s no xAxis label. You have to get the right label from your label array.

```
tooltips: {
    callbacks: {
      title: function(tooltipItem, data) {
        return sData.label[tooltipItem[0].index] // sData.label is your array with all data labels
      }
    }
  }
```

